# Document each environment variable this project consumes.
# Keep this file checked in; .gitignore ignores all other .env* files.

# Phase 2 — contact API route (src/pages/api/contact.ts).
# Database provisioned 2026-06-10: Upstash Redis `by-hris-contact-database`
# (free tier, GCP europe-west1). Values: Upstash console → database →
# Details → REST API. Set in Vercel (Production + Preview, token marked
# Sensitive) and in .env.local for local dev. The all-access default token
# gets swapped for an ACL-scoped token during Phase 2 execution.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
